h2 I want to donate, what’s next?
h3 How can I donate to this charity?
p First, choose how much you want to donate. Then click on “Review and make a payment”  to redirect you to the next page to complete your payment.
h3 When is the donation accepted?
p Once Paypal confirms the transaction (card and bank transfer confirmation is on the same day, lead slips to 4 working days to be confirmed).
